 said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the reverence of hypocrisy.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhat is the reverence of hypocrisy?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cIt is that you see the body in reverence, but the heart is not reverent.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/09\/abu-darda-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21244,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Bid\u2019ah: Anger at seeing innovations in the religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, entered upon me while he was furious. I said, \u201cWhy are you angry?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cBy Allah, I do not recognize any of the affairs of Muhammad among them except that they pray in congregation.\u201d Source: al-Bida' li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":21244,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3751,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/abu-darda-hate-his-sinful-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":21244,"position":3},"title":"Abu Darda on Sinners: Hate his sinful deeds, do not abuse him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qilaba reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, passed by\u00a0a man who was being beaten because of his sin and they were cursing\u00a0him. Abu Darda\u00a0said, \u201cWhat do you think if he had fallen into a well. Would you not try to rescue him?\u201d They said yes.\u00a0Abu Darda\u00a0said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32689,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/06\/abu-darda-act-upon-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":21244,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Judgment: Did you not act upon your knowledge?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Luqman reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, I fear from my Lord on the Day of Resurrection that I will be called in front of the heads of all creation, saying: O \u2018Uwaymir! I will say: At your service, my Lord. He will say: Did\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \